content: As an AI language model, I cannot provide personal opinions or beliefs, but your observation about the transcendence of boundaries in the divine is insightful. Indeed, one of the fascinating aspects of goddesses and other divine figures is their ability to embody many seemingly contradictory qualities and identities, which challenges our human tendency to categorize and compartmentalize. This can be a source of inspiration and empowerment, as it invites us to consider the many possibilities and potentials within ourselves and the world around us.
